[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說伏婬經",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西晉沙門法炬譯",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，婆加婆在舍衛城祇樹給孤獨",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "園。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼時，居士阿那邠祁至世尊所，到已禮世尊足，却住一面。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿那邠祁居士却住一面已，白世尊曰：",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯，世尊！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間有幾伏婬而可知者？",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b16_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「汝居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間有十伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為十？",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此居士，或一伏婬，非法行婬干彼，非法求婬干無所方便為苦已，亦不自安身，亦不安父母及妻子、客使奴婢、沙門婆羅門，不有益事，為善得善得生天上。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士，或一伏婬，非法求婬干彼，非法求婬干已，自安身、父母妻子、客使奴婢，而不施沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b24_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，非法求干彼，非法求干已，自安隱身、父母妻子、客使奴婢，能施沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863b28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求財，彼如法求財已，不自安樂身，不為父母、不為妻子、不為奴婢，亦不施沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士，是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求財，彼如法求財已，而自安樂身，及父母妻子奴婢，不施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c05_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求財，彼如法求財已，而自安樂身，及父母妻子奴婢，施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c08_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求財不干彼，如法求財不干已，亦不自安樂身，亦不為父母妻子奴婢，亦不施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求財不干彼，如法求財不干已，自得安樂身及父母妻子奴婢，不施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c15_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求財不干彼，如法求財不干已，自得安樂身，及父母妻子奴婢，施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼得錢財，於中染著、極染著，不見禍變，亦不知棄，而貪食之。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c19_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，如法求錢財不干彼，如法求錢財不干已，自得安隱身，及父母妻子奴婢，施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼得錢財，亦不染亦不著，亦不於中樂，亦不於中住，亦知是禍變，亦能棄捨而食之。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是一伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c25_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼或一伏婬，非法求錢財干彼，非法求錢財干已，亦不自安隱身，亦不安隱父母、妻子奴婢，亦不施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "伏婬我說此弊惡。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0863c29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一伏婬，非法求錢財干彼，非法求錢財干已，自安隱身，及父母妻子奴婢，不施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此伏婬此，伏婬此小勝小勝。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼或一伏婬，如法求錢財不干彼，如法求錢財不干已，自得安樂身，及父母妻子奴婢，施與沙門婆羅門，為善得善身生善處。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼得錢財，不染不著、不持不樂，知是禍變、棄捨離而食之。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "食婬最勝最妙、最上最好、無上勝。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶若，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有牛乳，因乳有酪，因酪有醍醐，因醍醐有酥，因酥有酪酥，此是最勝最妙無上說。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，居士！",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸伏婬如是伏婬，最勝最妙、極妙最上、無上無上。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說頌偈曰：",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「非法聚錢財，　　如法如法施；",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不施不食之，　　亦不施為福，",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二俱為慳濁，　　惡行食此婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如法求錢財，　　欲以施為福，",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦施及食之，　　亦能作福德，",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二俱不慳濁，　　皆有此伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有能行智慧，　　伏婬隨所行，",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知變有知足，　　知足而食之。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有能行智慧，　　最妙能伏婬。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛如是說，居士阿那邠祁聞世尊所說，歡喜而樂。",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說伏婬經",
        "from": "T01n0065_001:0864a25_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]